      <div id="results" class="hidden space-y-3 pb-10 sm:pb-14 reveal">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F8FAFC]">Game <span id="usernameDisplay" class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#22C55E] to-[#16a34a]"></span></h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.3)]">klik game untuk analisa</span>
        </div>
        <div id="gameList" class="space-y-2.5"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="faq" class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.01)]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 reveal">
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-[color:var(--brand)] uppercase mb-4">FAQ</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#F8FAFC] tracking-tight">Frequently Asked <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#22C55E] to-[#16a34a]">Questions</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3 reveal" id="faqContainer">
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false"><span>Apakah website ini gratis?</span><span class="faq-arrow"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Ya, 100% gratis selamanya. Tidak ada iklan, tidak ada batasan jumlah analisis, dan tidak memerlukan akun.</div></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false"><span>Bagaimana cara kerja analisisnya?</span><span class="faq-arrow"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Stockfish Engine berjalan langsung di browser kamu melalui Web Worker. Setelah kamu memilih game dari Chess.com, setiap langkah akan dievaluasi dan diklasifikasikan berdasarkan perbandingan dengan langkah terbaik engine.</div></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false"><span>Apakah data game saya disimpan?</span><span class="faq-arrow"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Tidak. Data game diambil langsung dari Chess.com API dan hanya diproses di browser kamu. Kami tidak menyimpan data apapun di server.</div></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false"><span>Menggunakan engine apa?</span><span class="faq-arrow"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Kami menggunakan Stockfish 10 &mdash; salah satu engine catur terkuat di dunia. Dengan analisis MultiPV depth 10 untuk mendapatkan 3 langkah terbaik di setiap posisi.</div></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false"><span>Apakah mendukung HP/smartphone?</span><span class="faq-arrow"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Ya, antarmuka kami responsif dan bekerja sempurna di semua perangkat &mdash; desktop, tablet, dan smartphone.</div></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false"><span>Apakah perlu akun Chess.com?</span><span class="faq-arrow"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Kamu hanya perlu memasukkan username Chess.com untuk mengambil game publik. Tidak perlu login atau memberikan password.</div></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false"><span>Berapa lama proses analisis?</span><span class="faq-arrow"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Tergantung panjang permainan. Rata-rata 5-15 detik untuk game 40 langkah. Analisis berjalan otomatis setelah game dipilih.</div></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false"><span>Apakah bisa digunakan offline?</span><span class="faq-arrow"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Tidak untuk saat ini. Karena game diambil dari Chess.com API, koneksi internet diperlukan. Namun engine berjalan di browser, jadi setelah game dimuat, analisis tetap berjalan.</div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="relative border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.04)] py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10 lg:gap-12">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-4"><span class="text-2xl" style="color:var(--brand)"><i class="fas fa-chess-knight"></i></span><span class="text-lg font-bold text-[#F8FAFC] tracking-tight">Chess<span style="color:var(--brand)">Review</span></span></div>
          <p class="text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.3)] text-sm leading-relaxed">Analisis permainan catur gratis menggunakan Stockfish Engine. Review lengkap untuk membantu kamu meningkatkan permainan.</p>
          <div class="flex gap-3 mt-5">
            <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.03)] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.04)] flex items-center justify-center text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] hover:border-[rgba(34,197,94,0.2)] transition-all no-underline"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
            <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.03)] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.04)] flex items-center justify-center text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] hover:border-[rgba(34,197,94,0.2)] transition-all no-underline"><i class="fab fa-discord"></i></a>
            <a href="mailto:hello@example.com" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.03)] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.04)] flex items-center justify-center text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] hover:border-[rgba(34,197,94,0.2)] transition-all no-underline"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div><h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-[#F8FAFC] mb-5">Navigation</h4><ul class="space-y-3"><li><a href="#" class="text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] transition-colors no-underline">Home</a></li><li><a href="#features" class="text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] transition-colors no-underline">Features</a></li><li><a href="/support" class="text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] transition-colors no-underline">Support</a></li><li><a href="/faq" class="text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] transition-colors no-underline">FAQ</a></li><li><a href="/contact" class="text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] transition-colors no-underline">Contact</a></li><li><a href="/about" class="text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] transition-colors no-underline">About</a></li></ul></div>
        <div><h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-[#F8FAFC] mb-5">Resources</h4><ul class="space-y-3"><li><a href="#" class="text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] transition-colors no-underline">Stockfish Engine</a></li><li><a href="#" class="text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] transition-colors no-underline">Chess.com API</a></li><li><a href="#" class="text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] transition-colors no-underline">Opening Book</a></li><li><a href="#" class="text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] transition-colors no-underline">PGN Reference</a></li><li><a href="#" class="text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] hover:text-[color:var(--brand)] transition-colors no-underline">Changelog</a></li></ul></div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-[#F8FAFC] mb-5">Stay Updated</h4>
          <p class="text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.3)] text-sm mb-4">Dapatkan update fitur terbaru dan tips catur.</p>
          <form id="newsletterForm" class="flex gap-2">
            <input type="email" id="newsletterEmail" required placeholder="email kamu" class="flex-1 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.03)] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] text-sm text-[#F8FAFC] outline-none focus:border-[rgba(34,197,94,0.3)] transition-all" style="font-family:inherit">
            <button type="submit" id="newsletterBtn" class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-[color:var(--brand)] text-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-[color:var(--brand-dark)] transition-all border-none cursor-pointer" style="font-family:inherit">Subscribe</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.04)] flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <p class="text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.2)] text-xs">Made with <i class="fas fa-heart"></i> &middot; Powered by Stockfish</p>
        <p class="text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.2)] text-xs">&copy; <span id="footerYear"></span> Chess Review. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
  (function () {
    'use strict';

    /* ---------- Toast helper ---------- */
    function showToast(message, type) {
      var container = document.getElementById('toastContainer');
      var toast = document.createElement('div');
      toast.className = 'toast ' + (type || 'success');
      var icon = type === 'error' ? 'fa-circle-exclamation' : 'fa-circle-check';
      toast.innerHTML = '<i class="fas ' + icon + '"></i><span>' + message + '</span>';
      container.appendChild(toast);
      setTimeout(function () {
        toast.style.transition = 'opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease';
        toast.style.opacity = '0';
        toast.style.transform = 'translateY(-8px)';
        setTimeout(function () { toast.remove(); }, 300);
      }, 3200);
    }

    /* ---------- Scroll progress + navbar state + back to top ---------- */
    var navbar = document.getElementById('navbar');
    var backToTop = document.getElementById('backToTop');
    var scrollProgress = document.getElementById('scrollProgress');
    function onScroll() {
      var s = window.pageYOffset;
      if (s > 40) navbar.classList.add('scrolled'); else navbar.classList.remove('scrolled');
      if (s > 600) backToTop.classList.add('visible'); else backToTop.classList.remove('visible');
      var docHeight = document.documentElement.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight;
      var pct = docHeight > 0 ? (s / docHeight) * 100 : 0;
      scrollProgress.style.width = pct + '%';
    }
    window.addEventListener('scroll', onScroll, { passive: true });
    onScroll();
    backToTop.addEventListener('click', function () { window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' }); });

    /* ---------- Smooth scroll buttons ---------- */
    document.querySelectorAll('[data-scroll-to]').forEach(function (btn) {
      btn.addEventListener('click', function () {
        var target = document.querySelector(btn.getAttribute('data-scroll-to'));
        if (target) target.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
      });
    });

    /* ---------- Mobile menu ---------- */
    var mobileMenu = document.getElementById('mobileMenu');
    var hamburger = document.getElementById('hamburger');
    var menuBackdrop = document.getElementById('menuBackdrop');

    function openMenu() {
      mobileMenu.classList.add('open');
      menuBackdrop.classList.add('open');
      hamburger.classList.add('active');
      hamburger.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');
      document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
    }
    function closeMenu() {
      mobileMenu.classList.remove('open');
      menuBackdrop.classList.remove('open');
      hamburger.classList.remove('active');
      hamburger.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
      document.body.style.overflow = '';
    }
    hamburger.addEventListener('click', function () {
      mobileMenu.classList.contains('open') ? closeMenu() : openMenu();
    });
    menuBackdrop.addEventListener('click', closeMenu);
    document.addEventListener('keydown', function (e) {
      if (e.key === 'Escape' && mobileMenu.classList.contains('open')) closeMenu();
    });
    document.querySelectorAll('.mobile-nav-link').forEach(function (el) {
      el.addEventListener('click', closeMenu);
    });

    /* ---------- FAQ accordion ---------- */
    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach(function (btn) {
      btn.addEventListener('click', function () {
        var item = btn.closest('.faq-item');
        var answer = item.querySelector('.faq-answer');
        var isActive = item.classList.contains('active');
        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item.active').forEach(function (el) {
          if (el !== item) {
            el.classList.remove('active');
            el.querySelector('.faq-answer').style.maxHeight = '0';
            el.querySelector('.faq-question').setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
          }
        });
        if (isActive) {
          item.classList.remove('active');
          answer.style.maxHeight = '0';
          btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
        } else {
          item.classList.add('active');
          answer.style.maxHeight = answer.scrollHeight + 'px';
          btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');
        }
      });
    });
    // Recalculate open FAQ height on resize (fixes stale max-height bug)
    window.addEventListener('resize', function () {
      var openItem = document.querySelector('.faq-item.active .faq-answer');
      if (openItem) openItem.style.maxHeight = openItem.scrollHeight + 'px';
    });

    /* ---------- Reveal-on-scroll ---------- */
    var reveals = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal, .reveal-zoom');
    if (reveals.length && 'IntersectionObserver' in window) {
      var observer = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
        entries.forEach(function (entry) {
          if (entry.isIntersecting) {
            entry.target.classList.add('visible');
            observer.unobserve(entry.target);
          }
        });
      }, { threshold: 0.08, rootMargin: '0px 0px -40px 0px' });
      reveals.forEach(function (el) { observer.observe(el); });
    } else {
      reveals.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('visible'); });
    }

    /* ---------- Footer year ---------- */
    document.getElementById('footerYear').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();

    /* ---------- Newsletter (demo only, no backend) ---------- */
    var newsletterForm = document.getElementById('newsletterForm');
    if (newsletterForm) {
      newsletterForm.addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        var email = document.getElementById('newsletterEmail').value.trim();
        var emailPattern = /^[^\s@]+@[^\s@]+\.[^\s@]+$/;
        if (!emailPattern.test(email)) {
          showToast('Masukkan alamat email yang valid', 'error');
          return;
        }
        var btn = document.getElementById('newsletterBtn');
        var orig = btn.textContent;
        btn.textContent = '...';
        btn.disabled = true;
        setTimeout(function () {
          btn.textContent = 'Subscribed!';
          showToast('Terima kasih sudah subscribe!', 'success');
          document.getElementById('newsletterEmail').value = '';
          setTimeout(function () { btn.textContent = orig; btn.disabled = false; }, 2000);
        }, 700);
      });
    }

    /* ---------- Chess.com search ---------- */
    var MONTHS = ['Januari', 'Februari', 'Maret', 'April', 'Mei', 'Juni', 'Juli', 'Agustus', 'September', 'Oktober', 'November', 'Desember'];
    var now = new Date();
    var curMonth = now.getMonth();
    var curYear = now.getFullYear();

    var $month = $('#month');
    MONTHS.forEach(function (name, i) {
      var val = String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0');
      $month.append('<option value="' + val + '" ' + (i === curMonth ? 'selected' : '') + '>' + name + '</option>');
    });

    var $year = $('#year');
    for (var y = curYear; y >= 2005; y--) {
      $year.append('<option value="' + y + '" ' + (y === curYear ? 'selected' : '') + '>' + y + '</option>');
    }

    var USERNAME_PATTERN = /^[a-zA-Z0-9_-]{2,25}$/;
    var $username = $('#username');
    var $usernameError = $('#usernameError');

    function setFieldError(msg) {
      $usernameError.text(msg || '');
      $username.toggleClass('input-error', !!msg);
    }
    $username.on('input', function () { setFieldError(''); });

    function escapeHtml(str) {
      return String(str).replace(/&/g, '&amp;').replace(/</g, '&lt;').replace(/>/g, '&gt;').replace(/"/g, '&quot;');
    }

    function renderGame(game, username) {
      var white = (game.white && game.white.username) || '?';
      var black = (game.black && game.black.username) || '?';
      var result = (game.white && game.white.result) || (game.black && game.black.result) || '*';
      var date = game.end_time ? new Date(game.end_time * 1000).toLocaleDateString('id-ID') : (game.end_date || '-');
      var iconMap = { blitz: 'fa-bolt', rapid: 'fa-stopwatch', bullet: 'fa-rocket', daily: 'fa-calendar-day' };
      var timeIcon = iconMap[game.time_class] || 'fa-trophy';
      var isUserWhite = white.toLowerCase() === username.toLowerCase();
      var userResult = isUserWhite ? (game.white && game.white.result) : (game.black && game.black.result);
      var resultColor = userResult === 'win' ? 'text-[color:var(--brand)]' : (userResult && userResult !== 'win' ? 'text-[color:var(--danger)]' : 'text-[color:var(--warn)]');
      var opponent = isUserWhite ? black : white;
      var pgn = game.pgn || '';
      if (!pgn) return false;

      var card = document.createElement('div');
      card.className = 'game-card';
      card.setAttribute('tabindex', '0');
      card.setAttribute('role', 'button');
      card.setAttribute('aria-label', 'Analisa game ' + white + ' vs ' + black);
      card.innerHTML =
        '<div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">' +
          '<div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 min-w-0">' +
            '<span class="text-xl flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--brand)"><i class="fas ' + timeIcon + '"></i></span>' +
            '<div class="min-w-0">' +
              '<p class="text-[#F8FAFC] font-semibold text-sm sm:text-base truncate">' +
                (isUserWhite ? '<span style="color:var(--brand)">&#x25CF;</span> ' : '') +
                escapeHtml(white) + ' <span class="text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.3)] mx-1">vs</span> ' + escapeHtml(black) +
                (!isUserWhite ? ' <span style="color:var(--brand)">&#x25CF;</span>' : '') +
              '</p>' +
              '<p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.4)] truncate">' + date + ' &mdash; ' + escapeHtml(game.time_class || '-') + ' (' + (game.rated ? 'Rated' : 'Casual') + ')</p>' +
            '</div>' +
          '</div>' +
          '<div class="text-right flex-shrink-0">' +
            '<p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold ' + resultColor + '">' + escapeHtml(result) + '</p>' +
            '<p class="text-xs text-[rgba(248,250,252,0.3)] truncate max-w-[100px]">vs ' + escapeHtml(opponent) + '</p>' +
          '</div>' +
        '</div>';

      function goToGame() { window.location.href = '/game?pgn=' + encodeURIComponent(pgn); }
      card.addEventListener('click', goToGame);
      card.addEventListener('keydown', function (e) {
        if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') { e.preventDefault(); goToGame(); }
      });
      document.getElementById('gameList').appendChild(card);
      return true;
    }

    function renderEmptyState(message) {
      $('#gameList').html(
        '<div class="empty-state"><i class="fas fa-chess-board"></i><p>' + escapeHtml(message) + '</p></div>'
      );
    }

    function setSearchLoading(isLoading) {
      var $btn = $('#searchBtn');
      $btn.prop('disabled', isLoading);
      $('#searchBtnIcon').html(isLoading ? '<span class="spinner" style="width:16px;height:16px;border-width:2px"></span>' : '<i class="fas fa-search"></i>');
      $('#searchBtnText').text(isLoading ? 'Mencari...' : 'Cari Game');
    }

    $('#searchForm').on('submit', async function (e) {
      e.preventDefault();

      var username = $username.val().trim();
      if (!username) { setFieldError('Username tidak boleh kosong'); $username.trigger('focus'); return; }
      if (!USERNAME_PATTERN.test(username)) { setFieldError('Username hanya boleh huruf, angka, garis bawah, dan strip'); $username.trigger('focus'); return; }
      setFieldError('');

      var month = $('#month').val();
      var year = $('#year').val();

      $('#loading').removeClass('hidden');
      $('#error').addClass('hidden');
      $('#results').addClass('hidden');
      $('#gameList').empty();
      setSearchLoading(true);

      try {
        var res = await $.getJSON('/api/proxy/games/' + encodeURIComponent(username) + '/' + year + '/' + month);
        $('#loading').addClass('hidden');
        $('#usernameDisplay').text(username);

        if (!res.games || res.games.length === 0) {
          renderEmptyState('Tidak ada game ditemukan untuk bulan ini');
        } else {
          var games = res.games.slice().reverse();
          var rendered = 0;
          games.forEach(function (game) {
            if (renderGame(game, username)) rendered++;
          });
          if (rendered === 0) {
            renderEmptyState('Game ditemukan, tapi tidak ada data PGN yang bisa dianalisis');
          }
        }
        $('#results').removeClass('hidden');
        document.getElementById('results').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
      } catch (err) {
        $('#loading').addClass('hidden');
        var msg = 'Gagal mengambil data. Silakan coba lagi.';
        if (err && err.responseJSON && err.responseJSON.error) msg = err.responseJSON.error;
        else if (err && err.status === 404) msg = 'Username tidak ditemukan di Chess.com';
        else if (err && err.status === 0) msg = 'Tidak dapat terhubung ke server. Periksa koneksi internet kamu.';
        $('#errorMsg span').text(msg);
        $('#error').removeClass('hidden');
        showToast(msg, 'error');
      } finally {
        setSearchLoading(false);
      }
    });

  })();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
